          "id": "d714145b74e21056eb1d7a8bbccda583e86874e4",
          "message": "fix: dashboard concurrency scaling use Total Tput, add MiniMax-M2.5, optimize topK (#412)\n\n- Fix Concurrency Scaling chart to use Total Token throughput instead of\n  Output throughput for consistency with other dashboard metrics\n- Add MiniMax-M2.5 model to benchmark matrix (tp=2)\n- Remove c=256 from 8k/1k nightly params\n- Remove HSA_NO_SCRATCH_RECLAIM from Kimi config\n- Cache is_fused check in topK to avoid redundant function calls",
